ind, D., Balachandran, N., Lean, J., Lonergan, P., Solar cycle variability, ozone and climate (1999) Science, 284, pp. 305-308; Skoug, R.M., Gosling, J.T., Steinberg, J.T., McComas, J.T., Smith, C.W., Ness, N.F., Hu, Q., Burlaga, L.F., Extremely high solar wind: 29-30 October 2003 (2004) Journal of Geophysical Research, 109, pp. A09102. , 10.1029/2004JA010494; Srivastava, N., Predicting the occurrence of super-storms (2005) Annals of Geophysics, 23 (9), pp. 2989-2995; Stokes, G.M., Schwartz, S.E., The atmospheric radiation measurement (ARM) program: Programmatic background and design of the cloud and radiation test bed (1994) Bulletin of the American Meteorological Society, 75 (7), pp. 1201-1221; Thayer, G.D., An improved equation for the radio refractive index of air (1974) Radio Science, 9, pp. 803-807; Thejll, P., Lassen, K., Solar forcing of the northern hemisphere land air temperature: new data (2000) Journal of Atmospheric and Solar-Terrestrial Physics, 62, pp. 1207-1213; Tsurutani, B.T., Mannucci, A.J., Iijima, B., Guarnieri, F.L., Gonzalez, W.D., Judge, D.L., Gangopadhyay, P., Pap, J., The extreme 2003 solar flares (and Bastille Day, 2000 Flare), ICMEs and resultant extreme ionospheric effect: a review (2006) Advances in Space Research, 37 (8), pp. 1583-1588; van Geel, B., Raspopov, O.M., Renssen, H., van der Plicht, J., Dergachev, V.A., Meijer, H.A.J., The role of solar forcing upon climate change (1999) Quaternary Science Reviews, 18, pp. 331-338; Veselovsky, I.S., Panasyuk, M.I., Avdyushin, S.I., Solar and heliospheric phenomena in October-November 2003: causes and effects (2004) Cosmic Research, 42 (5), pp. 453-508; Vey, S., Dietrich, R., Jonhsen, K.-P., Miao, J., Heygster, G., Comparison of tropospheric water vapour over Antarctica derived from AMSU-B data, ground-based GPS data and the NCEP/NCAR reanalysis (2004) Journal of the Meteorological Society of Japan, 82 (1 B), pp. 259-267; Wang, J., Zhang, L., Dai, A., 2005. Global estimates of water-vapor-we